Text: That should be enough for now.
We are come to deliver you unto darkness eternal...
There is no escape from death!
In death, you will find salvation!
Let us return, before we are waylaid any further.
If you value your life, flee while you still can!
A moment's hesitation and she will tear you apart!
I can only pray she forgets about me...
I think I can make it back by myself. Thank you.
Put down as many as you can!
Gizamaluks! A whole horde of them!
They must be looking for a place to nest.
We must keep them away from the ruins!
They only gather like this when preparing to nest.
Now there is nothing to stop them from defiling the ruins.
Let us withdraw for now and try to find another way.
Do you think we have seen the last of them?
Come. Let us continue our patrol.
Where are my sisters when I need them?
Why must they take so many!?
We shall need to guard this entrance more carefully from now on.
Thank you, for all you have done.
Is that all of them, I wonder?
Do you have any more of the artifacts?
If you find any more, please give them to me!
The wood raiders still have some of the relics!
They may only be deer, but do not underestimate them!
I wish you would stop worrying!
Would you care to join me on a hunt?
You have been practicing for this moment, have you not?
I will try not to disappoint you.
You worry overmuch. Just remember your training.
Perhaps it was too soon for you.
With a little help from our friend here.
Yes, and I am very thankful.
When next we hunt, you shall face your prey alone.
But what is it doing here?
It must have mistaken us for intruders...
We had best inform the others.
Perhaps we need to replace the core.
Ox'Gatorl, hear our prayer! Stop this madness!
We shall not succumb to the likes of you!
How could I have been so foolish!?
May my aim be straight and true!
You cannot hope to defeat us!
I have nothing left to give...
Your time is close at hand...
The moment I have been waiting for...
When all else is dust, I shall remain.
The earth opens up to claim you, mortal.
I must sssay, it has been much harder to fish of late.
Can I interessst you in some work?
When the clutchmother is happy, all of us are happy.
What a paltry ssselection of pearls!
I need as much coral as I can carry!
No sssuch thing as too much!
Thank you! Now for the next part of the plan.

Do not waver!
Defend the Round!

Your fashion sense
is bad, and you
should feel bad!

All that lives
will someday die!

Your face! It's
breaking my immersion!
I'm taking you in for questioning.
No time to catch our breath...
There shhhould be plenty in this cave!
I hope we do not encounter any...trouble.
Benthos! What are you doing here!?
I will not die so easily!

Not good!
Hold on, I'm coming!
I can sssmell those shhhells from here!
Perhaps thisss was a bad idea?
Hopefully, that was the lassst of them. Many thanksss!

Well, I suppose
you're not wrong...

What a waste
of my time...

I don't even
know why I care!

I-I've never been
so scared in
all my life...

To think that
was once a man...

Today's catch
smells a bit...riper
than usual.

Wait, that's not
the stink of fish!

I heard screams!
Are you─
what's that smell?

Draw your weapons!
And try not to breathe!

The smell is gone!
Or my nose has
stopped working!

I'll take either,
at this point.
...Wait, what's that?

I guess its
nose still works...

<pant> Let's leave
before anything
else shows up.

It's too strong!
Grab the fish
and run!
The treasure is mine! All mine!

Must find...the ship...
Forget the crew...

What did I do to
deserve such attention?
Your fight is with me, Andreia!

Massive draco. Right.
Here we go, then!
You can do it, finlesss one!
Perhapsss this was a bad idea!
They may be lurking in the shhhadows!
I am not well-sssuited to all of this violence!
Weakling! You dare shhhow your face!?
You are a fool to challenge usss!

Maybe charging the
huge draco was
a bad idea...

But I can't
<huff> just let it
run amok...

We did it!
I can't thank
you enough!

Hardly palatial,
but could be worse.

In spittin' distance
of the Crystarium, too.
Maybe our prey'll come to us!

But don't think
your petty heroism
will save you.

You thralls to morality
are pathetic.

Leave Lakeland to
the true sinners.

I think I heard─
There! It's them!

Nightshade!? And so
close to the Crystarium...

These lands are not
yours to claim!

Seems we're rid of
them for the time being.

Pray we don't happen
upon any more.

We're taking too
many losses! Retreat!

Draw your weapons!
We've got company!

Crystarium's got plenty
of fools to playact
the hero, I see.

Always did love
a good farce!

Just know that
you will never
have won.

We are Nightshade
and we will not
be forgotten!

This blighted world is
our inheritance.

No time to worry
about it now!

We managed to
drive them off.
Let me take care of that!
There'll be nothing left to bury!

So it's come to this...
No choice but to use Final Bastion!

They have our cousin!
Release the TERROR!
Witness the dawn of a new era!

Fire the forges! Tonight we
build an army!
Brave adventurers, enkindle the flames of the Bombard with your dance!

All that work!
Reduced to rubble!

Did anyone bother
to draft blueprints?
We'll be back! Just you wait!
Of all the times for them to appear!
Right on top of the tracks, too...
No choice but to kill them all. Or have sssomeone else do it...
Thank you! Now to investigate those tracks.
These marks were left by some sort of mouth... A very large one.
These are the remains of itsss prey. This warrants a closer look...
Is there no end to them!?

Alack, the timber
is fighting back!
That is the biggest one I have ever ssseen!
And that is Zumshs Aath Deepdread, the worst of them all!
I do not fancy our chances...
We do not know unlesss we try!
Spirits of my ancessstors, watch over me!
To think that we could triumph over Zumshs Aath Deepdread!
Red fragments of sssome sort... Perhaps the ssstories were true?
I was a fool to even attempt thisss!
Yesss! Another ssstep closer to finding that beassst!
Archaeotania shhhall be mine to command!
Ssspineless weaklings, the lot of you! Retreat!
Oh, I remember now. Thisss is cubus territory...
Thanksss to you, I was able to gather some ussseful clues.
It is a matter of time before I find Archaeotania!

Hm? What breaks
through yonder─ AUGH!

Did you think we'd
just let you go
on your merry way?

Ahem. As I harvested,
lonely as a cloud─

No, let me guess.
You were attacked. Again.

Will you require
an escort back
to the Crystarium?

Ah, chivalry!
The truest art.
Please do.

That's what I get
for being distracted...

I can do no more.
We must flee!

I have not yet
shuffled off this
mortal coil? Huzzah!

We should make
haste lest any
more are about.

Ha! That's right,
run back to your
precious refuge.

Take your “victory.”
Just remember, you'll
never be safe.

There's nowhere
in this world
you can run.

Lali-ho, lali-ho,♪
It's off to work, I go.♪

Maybe I'll stumble across
some ore on the way home...
It is no good... The Cupsss are doomed...
Look! I brought your favorite coral!
Not when I am ssso close!
I must provide what succor I can...
Ha ha! Thanksss for doing our job for usss!
You think you have me beaten!?
Now go, as fast as you can!
Our allies will see you to safety!
That was easier than I thought!
We shhhall feed you to Archaeotania!
I will not bow to the likes of you!

Hm... I may need
some bigger cogs...

And the actuator will
require additional tuning...

Overall, I'd say this test
was a rousing success!

Ah, I'm bleeding again.
Rather heavily!

<sigh> Hang on─
I'll staunch the wound.

And here come
the dracones. Naturally.

Don't mind me.
Just being savaged
by dracones here.

Why does this
always happen to me?

We'll be on
our way! Now
where's that knife...

No, no more
touching sharp objects!

Yes, yes! These readings
will prove invaluable!

I am here, foul Goggs!
Tremble before my masterpiece!

Wait... One, two, three, four─
Dastards! Have you no honor!?

Bwahahaha! Says the dwarf
who brought only one doll!
We'll melt her down to scrap!
That's not fair! You had help!

Have you no honor,
cheating Tholl!

You'll pay, interloper!
Don't think you won't pay!

Run, cowards! And next time
bring a bigger army!
Perhaps you would be game for a game, yes?
I call it “Kill or Be Killed!”
The rules are, as you can imagine, rather simple...
Not interested? I can't say I blame you!
I have to say, I'm rather good at this game!
I say, have you played this before?
Well, I think that's enough for one day! Ta-ta for now!
Go and be finlesss somewhere elssse!
My curse will consume you from within!

In life and in death
I serve Ronka...

Forever bound to this
place by sacred pact...

For the empire...
For the emperor...
I am sure thisss is the place.
Those benthos beat us to it...

What happened here?
Were you attacked?

Hahaha! Oh, you
righteous fools are
too easy to snare.

You're just so
predictable. Ha...
Haha... Ahahaha!

You will never
belong here.
Not like us.

Keep your peace.
It won't save you.

That could've gone
much worse, if you
hadn't come along.

I ought to
have known better.

Nightshade never tires
of dirty tricks.

Get moving. We
don't have the time
to waste here.

You made a
hash of it, then?

Look, we had
the same problem
with the strongholds...

The arrogance of
the Crystarium's ignorant
knows no bounds.

Well, we'll have to
see to that.

Let's make sure
they get what's
coming to them.

These lands were
always ours. Now
more than ever.
The finlesss ones and their pathetic friends shhhall perish!
The mighty one will sssup on your fleshhh!
You would unleash that evil upon the Tempessst!?

You go on ahead.
I will hold them off here!
I do believe it's time that I took center stage!
Have care. We know not what lies within...
Perhaps there's a pattern to their movements.
I must ask that you refrain from wandering...

Oh, I wouldn't dream of it!
La la la♪

It'll be finished when I say
it's finished, and I say it's
not finished! At least not yet.

Well, let me know when it is!
I don't want to miss when we
crush the Tholls!

Who goes there!?
A Tholl spy!?

Help! Someone! Anyone!
I'm too short to die!
Not the beard! Not the beard!

They've got us by the beard!
To the hills!

That will teach you to
stick your beard in Gogg
business!

You won't see me again!
I swear it!

These legs can only carry us
so far. We must fight!
The battle is lost! Fall back, fall back!

I knew it! The Goggs are
up to no good!

Any friend of the Tholls
is an enemy of ours!
Let seep sorrow into your heart.

Our secret weapon is
almost complete!

You may have defeated us
today, but tomorrow shall be ours!

Tell me your plan or I'll
have your helm!
Not if you're rotting in our gaol!

You wouldn't stab a dwarf
in the back now, would you?

Run today, live to
fight another day!
You are out of your element!
Wake up! Wake up, damn you!
I don't think I've ever seen anywhere so peaceful and serene.
Ha ha! I will give it some thought.

Oh, Gridania is a wonderful
place indeed! You should
stay a while.
I hope Editha is all right!
Please, take good care of her.

If you require my assistance,
do not hesitate to ask!
Editha, you mustn't run off like that again!

Do you know who could
be behind these attacks?
Yes, I think we've gathered that much...
Glad to see the threat of assassination has done little to dampen your mood.

Are you alright?
You've gone pale...

Ah...
Your eyes tell the tale.
We were too slow to save them!

We free their souls.
That is all we can do...

I feel my skin prickling.
What is this boiling aether...?
The manor house is just up ahead!

We are close...
Be on your guard!
As is the source of this suffocating aether...

The sheer power...
I can sense its strength from here!

Gods...
This must be the Warden!
...We stand in the presence of a Lightwarden.
Aye, this is the true scourge of Lakeland!

Are they preparing
for an assault?

Everyone at the ready!
We strike first!

How noble of you
to come to us!

We'll put you
out of your misery!

Now you see
the futility of
the good.

The only glory
is in sin!

Only the wicked
will walk these lands!

There are too
many of them!

Only the elves
truly know this world
we have created.

You were never
going to succeed.

We just don't
have the numbers...

What will become
of Lakeland now?

I can't believe
they had wargs...
Echoes, I think. But there is something strange about them.
Bows, with me! We have work to do!
It seems that they are diseased.
We must cull them before the sickness can spread.
We have allowed too many of them to escape...
Perhaps we will find some of them on our patrol.
Bows! It is time to leave!
Those crawlers must be what is spreading the disease!
My thoughts exactly. Sisters, you know what to do.
That should put a stop to the disease.
We are running dangerously low on arrows, though.
I suggest that we go and gather feathers for flights.
We let too many of them get away.
These tarichuks are tougher than they look...
I had best stop there. No point dying for a bunch of feathers.
This should suffice. Your assistance is much appreciated.
That is enough for the time being.
I will take those feathers off of your hands!
Bring me as many feathers as you can. It matters not how you get them.
Keep your eyes peeled for trouble.
They are attacking the ancient guardian!
To think that the ancient guardian could be defeated...
There is little more we can do here. Let us return.
It seems the danger has passed.
Come. We must report this to the others.
Did you hear that? It sounded like a roar...
If that is what I think it is, we must hurry!
Many a sister has died fighting that beast.
It is heading towards the village!
Quickly, there is no time to lose!
We have it running for its life. Now is our chance!
Sisters, we shall fight to the last!
This must be one of its defenses.
Do not get too close, sisters!
Your reign of terror has lasted long enough.
May the fallen rest in peace.
For now. Though Tojil is slain, our work is never done.
Let us return to the village.
We cannot allow the disease to spread!
Get them away from the ancient guardian!
Those that threaten the forest must perish!

Careful, mortal!
The bees are
everywhere...

It's not much,
but I'm not
going over there...

In fact, let's leave.
Quickly. Yes.

I'll just start
backing away slowly...

Let's get the
herbs and go.

Please...
My friend─he'll die
without these!

But you'll have
so much more
fun with us!

Now we can get
what we came for.

I can't go back
without the nectar...

At last, I can
go home and─

Oh no, Rukh
the giant bird!

I am never doing
nectar duty again...

If I didn't need that
nectar, I swear...

Now I can get to the
Bookman's Shelves.

Hello, pixies!
It's time to play.

What ever shall
we do today?

They do look
ever so peaceful...

...and that won't do,
will it now?

Hmm, I believe
it is time we
took our leave.

We would thank
you for the fun...

...if only you
weren't quite
so dull!

I daresay we
shall find better
sport elsewhere.

They're doubtless off
to trouble some
other poor soul.
I'll keep an eye on them.

We shall have
to find out!

A wee bit of
this, and...yes!

Oh dear. Are
you quite alright?

I say! That's
rather painful, sir!

I suppose we
have our answer.

It wasn't even a
funny prank! Unacceptable!

They're not amused?
I'm not amused...

Perhaps this fellow
can be of assistance.

Oh, dear, would
you look at that...

It will take ages
to collect more...

Our persistent pixie.
What a lovely surprise!
You stop this nonsense at once!

Oho, they seem
to be keeping up.
Shall we give them a chance?

A magicked tree?
What do you take me for?
If we were to be honest...
But there is time for sport yet!
You are an entertaining lot indeed.
Oh, no. Not yet, I think!

But perhaps if you
follow us south...

But I do hope
they'll do better
than a tree.

We are so pleased
to have you here...

Much more entertaining
than we expected.

If only I could say
the same for you.

You haven't seen
the half of us yet!
Ha! Fuath tricks don't scare me!

Now I teach you
a thing or two!
But wouldn't the Bookman's Shelves be a more appropriate venue?

I thought you
might say that!
...and it turns out we're not quite done...
Now, if you'll just come this way...
At this point, it seems only fair to mention...

...that we save for
very special occasions.
We'll have great fun either way, of course.

I don't doubt that.
You have terrible taste.
While there's still fun to be had?
But what a loss it was!

We really must do
this again sometime!
It seems we are the victors!
We thank you for the diversion...

You could at least
try to fight back.

A bit more savagery,
if you please.
